variables.name: startTimeMs
variables.comment:
* The start time (in milliseconds) to highlight the characters
         * specified by startChar and endChar.

variables.name: endTimeMs
variables.comment:
* The end time (in milliseconds) to highlight the characters
         * specified by startChar and endChar.

variables.name: startChar
variables.comment: * The offset of the start character to be highlighted

variables.name: endChar
variables.comment: * The offset of the end character to be highlighted
